sequenceDiagram
    participant A as User A
    participant B as User B
    participant Sync as Sync Server
    participant Async as Async Server
    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over A,Sync: SYNCHRONOUS: Users queue
        A->>Sync: add_expense(...)
        Note right of Sync: DB write (500ms)
        B->>Sync: get_expenses()
        Note right of Sync: User B BLOCKED<br/>waiting for A
        Sync->>A: "Expense added"
        Note right of Sync: NOW User B<br/>can proceed
        Sync->>B: {expenses: [...]}
    end
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over A,Async: ASYNCHRONOUS: Concurrent
        A->>Async: add_expense(...)
        B->>Async: get_expenses()
        Note right of Async: Both execute<br/>in parallel
        Async->>B: {expenses: [...]}
        Async->>A: "Expense added"
    end
